Class ShadowEGL14

java.lang.Object
org.robolectric.shadows.ShadowEGL14
@Implements(value=android.opengl.EGL14.class,
            minSdk=21)
public class ShadowEGL14
extends Object
Shadow for EGL14. Currently doesn't handle real graphics work, but avoids crashing when run.
